CraftTweaker - CraftTweaker allows modpacks and servers to customize the game. With CraftTweaker you can change recipes
ContentTweaker - Allows you to add Items and Blocks
Akashic Tome - The Book of Books. Store every documentation book in one.
CreateTweaker - Adds CraftTweaker support for Create
Custom Starter Gear - Gives you full control over what items players start the game with.
FTB Quests - Questing Mod by FTB
JAOPCA - Just A Ore Processing Compatibility Attempt
Ore Tweaker - Disable, tweak and add your own ore generation features using JSON for Minecraft Forge
PackMenu - A basic menu editor for modpacks.
Open Loader - An open source resource and data loader for Minecraft.
Property Modifier - Allows tweaking various properties of blocks and items. Also adds some other tweaks to aid
